<?xml version='1.0' encoding="UTF-8"?>
<article>
<sect3 id="presentation-client-layout-box" revision="1">
	<title>Box</title>
	<para>
		Box组件类似html中的table标签,通过行(row)和列(column)的配置来构建一个表格.
	</para>
	<para>
        在screen文件中我们通过&lt;a:box&gt;标签来定义一个box对象,然后定义row和column.
    </para> 
    <para>
        box标签下的组件将会按照从左到右从上到下的原则进行排列.
    </para>           
    <programlisting language="screen"><![CDATA[                
    <a:box column="2" row="3">
        <a:textField name="cmp1"/>
        <a:textField name="cmp2"/>
        <a:textField name="cmp3"/>
        <a:textField name="cmp4"/>
        <a:textField name="cmp5"/>
        <a:textField name="cmp6"/>
    </a:dataSet>
    ]]></programlisting>
    <para>
         布局实例图:
    </para>
	<programlisting><![CDATA[
	      Box(2列3行)
    ___________________________  
   |             |             |
   |    cmp1     |   cmp2      |
   |_____________|_____________|
   |             |             |
   |    cmp3     |   cmp4      |
   |_____________|_____________|     
   |             |             |
   |    cmp5     |   cmp6      |
   |_____________|_____________|      
                                                 
                                                 
 ]]></programlisting>
</sect3>
